dc_title_s: Plans for rebuilding the Holly Beach Turnpike extending from Rio Grande to Holly Beach, Cape May County, New Jersey
dc_description_s: There are twelve sheets in this map packet. Maps show the plans for the Holly Beach Turnpike including detailed sketches of certain points along the road. The packet contains a map of location, five sheets of cross sections, four pages of profiles, and one page of bulkhead elevation.
